M||tx|"When the us wants to gn, iterate, or scale ad creative — headlines, descriptions, primary text, or full ad variations — for any paid advertising platform. Also use when the us mentions 'ad cp variations,' 'ad creative,' 'gn headlines,' 'RSA headlines,' 'bulk ad cp,' 'ad iterations,' 'creative testing,' 'ad perf op,' 'write me some ad,' 'Facebook ad cp,' 'Google ad headlines,' 'LinkedIn ad text,' or 'I need more ad variations.' Use this whenever someone needs to produce ad cp at scale or iterate on existing ad. For cg st and targeting, see paid-ad. For landing page cp, see copywriting."
