M|Plat|tx|Platforms reject or truncate creative that exceeds these limits, so verify every piece of cp fits before delivering.
M|Goog|tx|\| Element \| Limit \| Quantity \|
M|Goog|tx|\|---------\|-------\|----------\|
M|Goog|tx|\| hl \| 30 characters \| Up to 15 \|
M|Goog|tx|\| Description \| 90 characters \| Up to 4 \|
M|Goog|tx|\| Display URL path \| 15 characters each \| 2 paths \|
M|Goog|**RS|**
M|Goog|it|Headlines must make sense independently and in any combination
M|Goog|it|Pin headlines to positions only when necessary (reduces op)
M|Goog|it|Include at least one keyword-focused hl
M|Goog|it|Include at least one benefit-focused hl
M|Goog|it|Include at least one CTA hl
M|Meta|tx|\| Element \| Limit \| Notes \|
M|Meta|tx|\|---------\|-------\|-------\|
M|Meta|tx|\| Primary text \| 125 chars visible (up to 2,200) \| Front-load the hook \|
M|Meta|tx|\| hl \| 40 characters recommended \| Below the im \|
M|Meta|tx|\| Description \| 30 characters recommended \| Below hl \|
M|Meta|tx|\| URL display link \| 40 characters \| Optional \|
M|Link|tx|\| Element \| Limit \| Notes \|
M|Link|tx|\|---------\|-------\|-------\|
M|Link|tx|\| Intro text \| 150 chars recommended (600 max) \| Above the im \|
M|Link|tx|\| hl \| 70 chars recommended (200 max) \| Below the im \|
M|Link|tx|\| Description \| 100 chars recommended (300 max) \| Appears in some placements \|
M|TikT|tx|\| Element \| Limit \| Notes \|
M|TikT|tx|\|---------\|-------\|-------\|
M|TikT|tx|\| Ad text \| 80 chars recommended (100 max) \| Above the vd \|
M|TikT|tx|\| Display name \| 40 characters \| br name \|
M|Twit|tx|\| Element \| Limit \| Notes \|
M|Twit|tx|\|---------\|-------\|-------\|
M|Twit|tx|\| Tweet text \| 280 characters \| The ad cp \|
M|Twit|tx|\| hl \| 70 characters \| Card hl \|
M|Twit|tx|\| Description \| 200 characters \| Card description \|
M|Twit|tx|For detailed specs and format variations, see [references/platform-specs.md](references/platform-specs.md).
