M|Gene|it|**im generation** — Nano Banana Pro (Gemini), Flux, Ideogram for static ad images
M|Gene|it|**vd generation** — Veo, Kling, Runway, Sora, Seedance, Higgsfield for vd ad
M|Gene|it|**Voice & audio** — ElevenLabs, OpenAI TTS, Cartesia for voiceovers, cloning, multilingual
