M|Iter|tx|---
M|Head|**St|**
M|Head|it|Specific ("Cut reporting time 75%") over vague ("Save time")
M|Head|it|Benefits ("Ship code faster") over features ("CI/CD pipeline")
M|Head|it|Active voice ("Automate your reports") over passive ("Reports are automated")
M|Head|it|Include numbers when possible ("3x faster," "in 5 minutes," "10,000+ teams")
M|Head|**Av|**
M|Head|it|Jargon the audience won't recognize
M|Head|it|Claims w/o specificity ("Best," "Leading," "Top")
M|Head|it|All caps or excessive punctuation
M|Head|it|Clickbait that the landing page can't deliver on
M|Desc|Desc|
M|Desc|it|Add proof points (numbers, testimonials, awards)
M|Desc|it|Handle objections ("No credit card required," "Free forever for small teams")
M|Desc|it|Reinforce CTAs ("Start your free trial today")
M|Desc|it|Add urgency when genuine ("Limited to first 500 signups")
M|Desc|tx|---
